      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;../../assets/images/wiapost/5089-Suffering-And-Remedy.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Suffering And Remedy&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
